  }), mdx("p", null, "The item tower is straightforward where embeddings from multiple attributes (e.g., title, brand, seller) are concatenated into a single vector (this is similar to Amazon\u2019s approach though they have embeddings for each attribute). Then, the vector goes through multiple ", mdx("a", {
